## PROJECT REALITY (Ground Truth — DO NOT generalize beyond this)

**Project Name:** LDM 2.0 — Academic ERP & Ayurveda/Healthcare Course Management System  
**Deployed On:** Vercel  
**Tech Stack:**
- **Framework:** Next.js 16 (App Router, React 19, TypeScript 5)
- **Database:** MongoDB via Mongoose 9
- **Auth:** NextAuth.js v4 — JWT strategy, credential + Google OAuth provider
- **File Storage:** Cloudinary (images, PDFs, DOCX, PPTX, XLSX, brochures)
- **Email:** Nodemailer (OTP-based email verification)
- **Animations:** Framer Motion (page transitions, staggered list rendering)
- **Testing:** Jest (unit) + Playwright (E2E)
- **Analytics:** Vercel Analytics (@vercel/analytics)
- **Client-side PDF:** jsPDF + html2canvas + html2pdf.js

**Real Models in the Codebase (35 total):**
- [User](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/User.ts#5-35) — roles: admin, teacher, student, employee | statuses: active, pending, under_review, rejected, suspended
- [Program](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/Academic.ts#62-82) — contains embedded `PricingSubSchema` + `CurriculumSubSchema` (a deeply nested schema with `detailed_syllabus`, `practical_procedures`, `case_scenarios`, `internship`, `assessment`)
- [Session](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/Academic.ts#83-89), [Subject](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/Academic.ts#90-99), [Batch](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/Academic.ts#100-117), [Assignment](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/Academic.ts#118-126) — all defined in single [Academic.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/Academic.ts) file
- `Attendance` — daily per-subject attendance, upsert pattern by date+subject+section
- [Result](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/Result.ts#9-23) — per exam-type per subject per batch, with `is_published` gate and compound unique index
- [FeeRecord](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/FeeRecord.ts#15-31) — immutable `baseCoursePrice` locked at admission, embedded `PaymentEntry[]` array
- `FeeStructure`, `FeePayment`, `StudentFee`, `Expense`, `Salary` — full finance module
- [Notice](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/Notice.ts#5-23) — supports `file_type: 'none' | 'rich-text' | 'md' | 'pdf' | 'docx' | 'pptx' | 'xlsx'`
- [LibraryDocument](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/LibraryDocument.ts#3-18), `LibraryCategory`, `DocumentVersion`
- [DocumentRequirement](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/DocumentRequirement.ts#35-57) — with `scope: { type: 'all'|'program'|'batch'|'student' }` and `custom_fields: ICustomField[]`
- `DocumentSubmission` — student submissions with `form_responses` JSON
- [AuditLog](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/AuditLog.ts#3-14) — immutable by pre-hook on `updateOne`/`deleteOne`, tracks field-level deltas
- [ProTest](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/Test.ts#27-46) (Test.ts) — MCQ exam engine with `shuffleQuestions`, `shuffleOptions`, `negativeMarking`, `resultMode: 'instant'|'manual'`
- `TestAttempt`, `TestAnswerKey`
- [JobPosting](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/JobPosting.ts#16-32) — with `eligibility` (program filter, graduation year, 10th/12th %) and `referral` config
- `JobApplication`, [JobReferral](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/JobPosting.ts#10-15), `Resume`
- `CollegeSettings`, `Gallery`, `SliderImage`, `MarqueeMessage`, `Contact`
- `CoursePricing`, `StudentProfile`, `StudentDocuments`, `EmailOTP`, `Class`

**Real API Surface (`/api` directory, 101+ routes):**
- `/api/admin/*` — 18 namespaces including: academic, batches, courses, documents (6 sub-routes), fees, finance (13 sub-routes), jobs (4 sub-routes), library (5 sub-routes), tests, users, settings, slider, marquee, notices, gallery, stats
- `/api/student/*` — 18 namespaces: dashboard, attendance, library, notices, documents, fees, tests, results, resume, jobs
- `/api/teacher/*` — 10 namespaces: dashboard, attendance, tests, results, assignments
- `/api/public/*` — 13 namespaces (unauthenticated): courses, notices, gallery, marquee, contact, course-pricing
- `/api/auth/*` — NextAuth handlers + OTP flows

**Real Middleware ([src/middleware.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/middleware.ts)):**
- Edge-level RBAC using NextAuth `withAuth` wrapper
- Blocks: admin APIs from non-admins, student APIs from non-students, teacher APIs from non-teachers
- Exception pattern: `/api/admin/tests` is shared with teacher role (checked inline)
- Exception pattern: `/api/student/notices` is shared with teacher role
- Student status guard: `pending`/`under_review` → redirect to `/pending-approval`
- Profile completion gate: `isProfileComplete === false` → redirect to `/complete-profile`

**Real Utility Libraries (`src/lib/`):**
- `db.ts` — Mongoose connection with global cache to prevent hot-reload connection leaks
- `rateLimit.ts` — In-memory rate limiter (IP-based, per-action namespaced Map), 60s cleanup cycle, Vercel-aware IP extraction from `x-forwarded-for`
- `auth.ts` — NextAuth config with JWT callbacks, session extension (role, status, isProfileComplete)
- `autoCreateStudentFee.ts` — Auto-generates `FeeRecord` on student approval
- `feeCalculator.ts` — Centralized fee math utility
- `checkEligibility.ts` — Job application eligibility checker
- `testSchemaValidator.ts` — MCQ test schema validation (800 lines)
- `uploadLimits.ts` / `uploadLimits.client.ts` — File size/type enforcement per category
- `validate.ts` — Shared form validation logic

**Public Website (`/app/(public)`):**
- Homepage (`page.tsx` — 31KB), Courses listing, Course detail (`[id]`), Gallery, Notices, Library (public), About, Team, Hospital, Ayurvedic Pharma, Collaborations, Facilities, Mission, Contact, Register, Why-Choose-Us, Vaid-Saurabh profile page

**Deployment Config (`next.config.ts`):**
- `generateBuildId` tied to `VERCEL_GIT_COMMIT_SHA` to prevent cache bleed across deployments
- Layered `Cache-Control` strategy: static assets → `immutable` (1 year), images → `86400s + SWR`, HTML pages → `no-cache, must-revalidate`
- Security headers: `X-Frame-Options: DENY`, `X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff`, `Strict-Transport-Security`, `Referrer-Policy`, `Permissions-Policy`
- Server action body limit: 4.5MB (matching Vercel's hard limit, with 0.5MB overhead for form fields)

